        <https://w3id.org/aims-leaf/ExperimentSampleRoleEnum#size_marker>,
        <https://w3id.org/aims-leaf/ExperimentSampleRoleEnum#standard>,
        <https://w3id.org/aims-leaf/ExperimentSampleRoleEnum#target> .

